snippet.title: Lost in Vivo Trailer
snippet.description:
Lost in Vivo is a psychological horror game from Akuma Kira. 

https://gamejolt.com/games/lost-in-vivo/191123
Original demo is playable now, full game releases on 10/20/18.

The music in the video is by Nolan Reese and is available here:
https://nolanreese.bandcamp.com/track/broken
